text: Itumbiara picticornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1872. It is known from Costa Rica, Nicaragua and Panama.BioLib.cz - Itumbiara picticornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1872
title: Itumbiara picticornis
